      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks and feels great on the road. It\u2019s ready for a new home and plenty more adventures. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
